Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,CONFESSION
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.79,0:01:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Light, there's another message\Nfrom the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It was sent to Sakura TV\Nand we intercepted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm told it's a video\Nand a journal this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I figured I should tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A journal?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that idiot up to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.77,0:01:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't he just wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.11,0:01:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted the journal shown on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.57,0:01:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:01:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,2006?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,These entries are from last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take a look at the entry\Nhe made on the 30th.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] "Confirmed our Shinigami\Nat the Tokyo Dome."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is probably supposed to mean\Nthat he's going to do it on May 30th.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.34,0:02:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If these were aired on TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,his intentions would be obvious\Nto anyone who sees it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[cackles]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Besides, he can't see my Shinigami\Nunless he touches my Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How's he planning to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,22nd - My friend and I showed off\Nour notebooks in Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Hey, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] I forget,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,why can't I see my own lifespan\Neven though I have Shinigami eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.61,0:02:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,MISA AMANE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.61,0:02:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you could tell me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans with Shinigami eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,only need to know\Nthe lifespan of their victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And just as we can't see\Nthe lifespan of others of our kind,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,humans who possess a Death Note\Ncannot see each other's lifespan
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-even with the eyes.\N-[Misa sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"May 22nd,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:03:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,my friend and I showed off\Nour notebooks in Aoyama."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If by "notebooks" he is referring to\Nour Death Notes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that's something\Nthat could only be understood by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And as for the police,\Nthey'll be distracted by May 30th entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"We confirmed our Shinigami\Nat the baseball game at the Tokyo Dome."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been intended for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm almost positive\Nthat the real message from this diary
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is the one regarding Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that's the case…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it real?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to be careful not to say too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Better to wait\Nand hear his opinion first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,all I can say for sure is\Nhe must be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's completely obvious he wants\Nto meet Kira at the home game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't he understand what would happen\Nif we aired this message?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It would create an immediate panic\Nand the game would have to be canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, it's so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[chewing] Mmm.\NI'm not even sure
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,how to deal\Nwith this whole situation anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:04:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If we make the diary public,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,then we'll be forced to make\Nsome kind of televised announcement
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,cancelling the game on the 30th.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we don't broadcast it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,we can be sure\Nthe Second Kira won't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't cancelling the game make him angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling what he'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankly, that's not a big concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,From what we have witnessed\Nit's safe to say
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the Second Kira admires the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave his word to the Kira we invented
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that he'd refrain from killing aimlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm inclined to believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I say we make it public
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and we air an announcement\Ncanceling the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, we'll announce
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that on May 30th\Nwe're gonna set up checkpoints
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,on all roads leading to the Tokyo Dome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll send a response\Nfrom our invented Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,something like "I understand,\Nand I agree to meet you there."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuzaki, you don't honestly expect\Nhim to go there
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,if we set up checkpoints\Naround the Dome, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that Kira\Nwould even consider it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's possible the other one might.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It all depends on how stupid he really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,However, assuming he is not\Nactually the idiot we think he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,there could be another message\Nhidden in this diary,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,one that's not so obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's a message here\Nwritten in some code
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that only people with this Shinigami power\Ncan understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,there would be no way for me\Nto decipher it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it would only make sense
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,for us to look into all of the places\Nthat were mentioned in the journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, 22nd,\Nhe's meeting a friend in Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The 24th,\Nmeeting another friend in Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to be prepared for the possibility\Nthat all of our efforts will be fruitless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep an eye out\Nfor people with notebooks in Aoyama,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and people in clothing stores in Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If this phony Kira skips up\Nand gets apprehended,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,at the very least\NI have to obtain his notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.26,0:05:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the worst-case scenario,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I may end up\Nhaving to kill everyone there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.14,0:05:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is place more surveillance cameras\Nin Aoyama and Shibuya
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,in the hopes that we might\Ncapture something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We should also arrange to have\Nundercover officers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in both locations on these dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I should probably go\Nto Aoyama and Shibuya
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,since I blend in with the crowd there,\Nyou know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I'll go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But Light…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be all right. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoyama and Shibuya are places\NI'd go anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, out of all of us
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd probably look the most natural\Nhanging out with Matsui there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the Second Kira would be there\Nlooking for Kira, not for the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Okay, we will talk\Nmore about our trips tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsui] Sounds good, Light.\NSee you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful getting home
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-[phone ringing]\N-[Matsui] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It never fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The second I'm out the door,\Nmy phone starts ringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] It's Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When you two are working together,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to keep a close eye on Light\Nthe entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And please keep this between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he still plans\Nto investigate Light
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,until the probability that he's Kira\Nreaches zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, dear. You're back quite late today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to keep the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm helping\Nwith the Kira investigation a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I was hanging out\Nwith my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Your...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sayu squeals] What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, you have a girlfriend now?\NWhat's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that surprising.\NI'm 18 and I'm in university now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You should look for a boyfriend, Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A boyfriend?\NWhat's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, aren't you going\Nto have any dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Actually, I’m still full\Nfrom room service at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.41,0:07:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[squeals] I can't believe\Nyou just said that to mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's this about a hotel?\NSound pretty suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to have a little talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh… Should have known
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd appreciate an answer\Nif you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If two Shinigami happen to meet\Nin the human world,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-are they allowed to speak to each other?\N-Hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I'm attached to a human,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say it's against the rules,\Nunless I have their permission first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no laws against it either,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so I guess it's possible
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that another Shinigami might talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So does that mean if this fake Kira's\NShinigami were to see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a chance he might mention the fact\Nthat you’re with me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and reveal that I'm Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] They probably wouldn't,\Nbut it depends on their personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And if this kind of situation did arise,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can assume that you'll act\Nthe way you normally do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I see another human\Nwith a Shinigami,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I definitely think\Nyou've got the right approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.06,0:08:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Uh… Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he really think this far ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Aoyama is a big area.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I was searching\Nfor possible meeting places
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,when I stumbled upon this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,On the 22nd,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:09:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a big event going on at the club\Nin Aoyama called the Note Blue
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoyama, Blue Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Note" and "blue." It's a code.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Well, well, if you ask me,\Nthat's pretty elaborate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He might be smarter than I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,which means I will have to be\Nthat much more careful from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, this Note Blue place\Nis definitely worth checking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point in going there,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,if you don't want him\Nto find out that you're Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think it's worth the risk?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsui] Uh… Excuse me. Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, these are some of my friends\Nfrom school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsui] Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] This is my cousin Taro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his first time ever in Tokyo\Nand he wants to see Aoyama and Roppongi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so I figured the least we could do\Nis show him a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. He also told me\Nhe is looking for a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, does anyone want to volunteer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-[laughter]\N-Hey, I never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt that anyone would ever suspect
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that there was a police detective\Nhanging around with these students.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,With all of us walking together like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,even if Ryuk is seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,no one would be able to tell\Nwhich one of us he's following.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also a good defense\Nagainst L's surveillance cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Not such a bad way to investigate, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to stay relaxed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and keep an eye on the entrance\Nof the Note Blue when it opens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"Moon" Yagami, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re the only one\Nwhose lifespan I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,LIGHT YAGAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Kira! I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.31,0:10:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought it would be\Nthis easy to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Rem. Time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You finally found him\Nand now you just want to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[girl] Well, I can't go up to him\Nand say "Hi, Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.\NI'm the one who sent you the messages"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,with all these people around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know his name now,\Nso I can easily find out all about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it's such a unique name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yagami, Light - Birthdate: Feb 28, 1989\NHeight: 179cm - Weight: 54kg
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,BLOOD TYPE: A
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Oh, it's written as "moon,"\Nbut read as "Light."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he sure is amazing.\NLook at all this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He won the national tennis championship
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,when he was in his second\Nand third years of junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave an address\Nas the freshman representative
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:12:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,at this year's entrance ceremony\Nat To-oh University.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find a picture of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but there won't be anyone else\Nwith the name like Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would have ever thought\Nthat Kira would be so young and handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything about him\Nis better than I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe how easy it was\Nto purchase this information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The world sure is a scary place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I even know his home address now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] So we were there both days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In Aoyama on the 22nd
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and in Shibuya on the 24th.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And we observed nothing of significance\Non either occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That leaves us with only\Nthe Dome on the 30th.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I didn't notice anyone\Nwho looked suspicious at the Note Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he serious about the Dome?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[beeping]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[Watari] Ryuzaki, apparently Sakura TV
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,has just received another message\Nfrom the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was postmarked on the 23rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Second Kira] I am happy to say\Nthat I have found Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,To all of the people
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,at the television station\Nand the police department,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:12:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:12:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I-- I-- Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Where? In Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,His Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have seen Ryuk\Nand picked me out of the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No… No, there's no way he could have known\Nwho Ryuk was attached to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I checked repeatedly\Nthat no one was following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the only possible event
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that would correspond with this tape\Nbeing mailed on the 23rd,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is the entry regarding Aoyama on 22nd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The only ones from the task force\Nwho went to Aoyama
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,are Matsuda and Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Light really Kira after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, there's no proof\Nit even happened in Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a disaster if he found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It most likely means that the two Kiras\Nare now cooperating with each other
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point I don't think\Nwe should jump to any conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Second Kira is only saying\Nthat he found him, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He may not have made contact yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami] Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's it come to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[slurps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...we have no choice\Nbut to communicate as the police
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,directly with the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:13:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to send a message?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The police need to reach out\Nto the copycat and offer him a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to negotiate with him\Nto see if we can get Kira's real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the last thing\Nyou wanted to hear, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea\Nhow the Fake Kira will react to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have no means of stopping the police\Nfrom sending this message.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[man on TV]\NIf Kira doesn't yet know your name,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it may not be too late for you,\Nprovided you're willing to cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you do, you must not\Napproach Kira out of curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Make no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira will kill you if you contact him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You will used and disposed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider your own life for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yours, like every other life,\Nhas an intrinsic value.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is your chance\Nto right past wrongs
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,by sharing what you know about Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Only you can help us\Nbring his reign of terror to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,To introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[rings the doorbell]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rem] So, this is what you meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, could that be your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome ho--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello and good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Misa Amane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I just came by to give Light\Nan important notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,he left at school earlier today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,C-- Could you wait here for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sayu calls out] Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Notebook? Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[door closes]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.89,0:15:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Um... Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Misa Amane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.73,0:15:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you might get worried\Nif you saw the message on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't take it anymore,\Nso I brought this... notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[trembling breath]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A Death Note…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the Fake Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-Huh?\N-[Light] Please, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Uh, you're sure it's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Mom, she came all this way\Nto return my notebook to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you make us some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I don't see why not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Sayu] Huh?\N-[Light] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sachiko and Sayu] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Um... thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you find me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh… I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You never made the Shinigami eye deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When you have the Shinigami eyes,\Nlike I do,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see most people's\Nname and lifespan just by looking at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you can't see the lifespan\Nof any person who possesses a Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:16:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to admit, even I wasn't aware\Nof that little detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now you've managed to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were careless.\NWhat if you'd been caught by the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they'd know everything about Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the police didn't catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I do as you say from now on,\Nthey will never be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, don't you need\Nsomeone to see L's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want, I could be your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you please make me your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.38,0:17:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If she finds out I'm manipulating her\Nand gets hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll probably kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The day you and I were in Aoyama,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.56,0:17:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,there were three times the usual number\Nof surveillance cameras around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who was in Aoyama on the 22nd\Nwould've definitely been caught on camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That includes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:18:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you and I were seen together,\Nit wouldn't look very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, even being here together\Nright now
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you'd understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,These are pictures of me\Nwhen I went to Aoyama that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure no one\Nwould recognize her from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about your fingerprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All those tapes you sent\Nto the TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They all had\Nthe same fingerprints on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but those aren't my fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I do these things\Nwithout thinking about them first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Up until recently\NI lived in the Kansai region.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had this friend\Nwho was into the occult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggested that we distribute\Nthis fake poltergeist video
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I had made\Nto a bunch of different TV shows,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of as a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And she agreed to help me with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I had her take care of\Nall of the dubbing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,so my fingerprints\Nwouldn't be on the tapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I took them from her,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,added the Kira graphic
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and recorded the message\Nwith that voice effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And this friend you made the tapes with,\Nwhere is she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you're doing this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want me to kill her,\Njust say so and I'll kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really still can't trust me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,then here, I'll even let you\Nhold on to my Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll just be holding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'd still be the rightful owner of it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and that means\NI get to keep my Shinigami eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, there's no way\NI could possibly kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I become a burden to you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,then you can just kill me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would she go this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But you might have removed\Nseveral pages from your Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You could be hiding them somewhere,\Nfor all I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so suspicious of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care, even if all you do\Nis use me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly one year ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,my parents were killed in a robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was home with them at the time.\NIt happened right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted that man\Nto pay for what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:19:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But the trial dragged on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Opinions started surfacing\Nthat he was being falsely accused.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira punished him\Nfor what he did to my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why Kira means everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira means everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All I wanted was the chance\Nto meet you one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I could thank you for what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, all these irrational moves
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,they're just he means for her\Nto meet Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, she got around surveillance cameras\Nwith ease
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and managed not to leave her fingerprints\Non the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not as stupid as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And she has promised\Nto obey me from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[breath trembling]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be your boyfriend, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.63,0:21:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can act like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The lengths you went to meet me,\Nto be of help to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,those eyes of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that you sacrificed half your life to get,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,will become my weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try my hardest to make you love me.\NI promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]